Sea, Hudson Bay, Kara Sea, Laptev Sea, and Yellow Sea. The remaining 54 LMEs considered here represented more than 68% of the world Ô¨Åsheries catches during 1950‚Äì2004. The selected resident non-migratory Ô¨Åshes and invertebrates corresponded to 90% of total catch in these LMEs during 1950‚Äì2004.

